=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後唔敢再喺小息屙尿<br />\n而家諗翻好撚驚 條友本身都成日蝦人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過樓主講得出黎都知你真係好大陰影<br />\n如果當事人都算有悔意嘅話<br />\n不如同佢講一講清楚<br />\n或者搵個信得過嘅人講吓<br />\n當係解開自己個心結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1f77cb0787093715f1a9a0687561dd0ab311b7","tid":1884581,"uid":333353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:07:45.000Z","msg":"會，因為唔知道有冇其他受害者，如果唔出聲，個人就有機會會繼續消遙法外，越嚟越多受害人。佢細個咁做，有機會到大個咗都係咁做，佢對幾多個人做過定淨係對你一個人做過，你係唔知。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e20137dea18fe6223233f209435f38bbe1744f9","tid":1884581,"uid":313630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T13:43:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7a50ec87464042ffd880548e940551709ca4fe","tid":1884581,"uid":208196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fbbaf2bd4567595cf87901008908468d0ec658e","tid":1884581,"uid":202569,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:42:23.000Z","msg":"唔會 依家追究其實係二度傷害<br />\n告佢又要記返起重組成件事 仲有一堆程序<br />\n就算告到又點？自己都經歷咗啦 點都賠唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T20:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你係車俾人非禮係咪會唔出聲果d人黎<br />\n你軟弱 唔好教壞其他人"},{"pid":"1693c2ca91b39d2faf44be2aff53032938cc971a","tid":1884581,"uid":46219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49e0c5981b55b3717e0fd92c5b3a051c79661740","tid":1884581,"uid":341196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:29:11.000Z","msg":"如果你小學比人性侵犯過，唔止一次，係同性同學，佢表面品學兼優，所以你果陣唔敢同人講，但係陰影留到宜家，宜家大個左唔再怕，你有機會，會唔會清